.blank
.fill
you'd want to start at the end and tear toward the top,laying the requests
on top of each other as you go,this will put the requests in numerical order
then the auto file, and process all goes on top,put together with a paper
clip.the command file (ex: 150ctupda)should be on top for easy access. now
you're ready to key the necessary input to process the requests.
.nofill
